the Texas Second Congressional District

31:09.767 --> 31:12.292
when I say our thoughts and
our prayers are with you.

31:12.370 --> 31:14.861
All the people of the Texas
Second Congressional District,

31:14.939 --> 31:16.304
you say? Yes, indeed, sir.

