there, sir. Let me be clear.

32:28.646 --> 32:30.807
The United States is
eager to assist you.

32:30.882 --> 32:31.940
No, you're not. You're not.

32:32.016 --> 32:33.711
Absolutely not. I went to Oxford

32:33.785 --> 32:35.082
and I know what that word means.

32:35.153 --> 32:37.383
