34:28.032 --> 34:29.897
All right, I'll do it.

34:30.168 --> 34:31.692
Thank you, Mr. Congressman.

34:31.768 --> 34:33.065
Mr. President.

34:38.676 --> 34:40.643
All right, you, come on.

34:43.047 --> 34:44.172
How did it go?

34:44.248 --> 34:45.510
Well, there were three of them.

34:45.583 --> 34:48.710
