by a Pakistani vaudeville team.

34:48.786 --> 34:50.117
You know you've pretty
much hit rock bottom

34:50.188 --> 34:51.882
when you've been told you
have character flaws by a man

34:51.956 --> 34:54.947
who hanged his predecessor
in a military coup.

34:55.025 --> 34:56.014
Can we go home now?

34:56.094 --> 34:58.756
