I'm sorry?

40:16.714 --> 40:18.341
The helicopters, Harold.

40:18.416 --> 40:21.852
Why ain't we giving them something
to shoot down them helicopters?

40:21.919 --> 40:25.411
The helicopters are a problem.

40:27.324 --> 40:28.655
You think?

40:29.460 --> 40:31.792
Congressman... They're
shooting at Soviet gunships

