44:32.936 --> 44:34.028
Okay.

44:35.272 --> 44:37.206
RECEPTIONIST: No problem. Thank you.

44:38.742 --> 44:39.902
He should be here any moment.

44:39.977 --> 44:42.639
Don't worry about me. I'm fine.

44:44.148 --> 44:45.877
Good morning. Good morning, Congressman.

44:45.949 --> 44:47.576
Welcome back. Yeah. Marla.

